Name: That First Touch of Natural Vitamin D in the Spring
Description:
Songs that give you that first sunshine vibe. 

Let’s redeem that ‘Butterfly’ win. So if you submit ‘Butterfly’ or ‘Here Comes the Sun’, you get shot into the sun.

Name: Songs about cars
Description: Songs about cars, not songs by The Cars

Name: Hard Times Music League passes the Bechdel Test
Description:
"The Bechdel test is a measure of the representation of women in film and other fiction. The test asks whether a work features at least two women who talk to each other about something other than a man."

Submit a song that best represents what the musical equivalent of this test might be.

Name: Wait, THEY released song?
Description: I didn't even know they made music!

Name: Greatest non-original soundtrack song
Description: This song wasn't written for the show/movie, but it fits perfectly with the scene or soundtrack.

Name: Secretly Not Canadian Records
Description: Bands that feel like they’re from Canada but aren’t
